sts in rows touching the sky and filling space. It was yoked to excellent horses adorned with gold chains and equipped with implements for war. The earth was resounding as it was driven as if to crush the enemy's army and its own army was happy.","words":[{"d":"सारथिः","m":"charioteer"},{"d":"हृष्टः","m":"delighted"},{"d":"परसैन्यध्रर्षणम्","m":"which can destroy enemy's army"},{"d":"गन्धर्वनगराकारम्","m":"like the shape of the abode of Gandharvas"},{"d":"समुच्छ्रितपताकिनम्","m":"with rows of excellent flags"},{"d":"परमसम्पन्नैः","m":"richly endowed"},{"d":"हेममालिभिः","m":"gold chains"},{"d":"वाजिभिः","m":"horses"},{"d":"युक्तम्","m":"best at work"},{"d":"युद्धोपकरणैः","m":"well equipped with implements for war"},{"d":"पूर्णम्","m":"round"},{"d":"पताकाध्वजमालिनम्","m":"flag posts as if touching आकाशम् the sky"},{"d":"ग्रसन्तमिव","m":"as if filling space"},{"d":"वसुन्धराम्","m":"earth"},{"d":"नादयन्तम्","m":"resounding"},{"d":"परसैन्यानाम्","m":"enemy army"},{"d":"प्रणाशम्","m":"crushing"},{"d":"स्वसैन्यस्य","m":"own army"},{"d":"प्रहर्षणम्","m":"happy"},{"d":"रावणस्यरथम्","m":"Ravana's chariot"},{"d":"क्षिप्रम्","m":"with speed"},{"d":"चोदयामास","m":"drove"}]},{"v":4,"dev":"समापतन्तंसहसास्वनवन्तंमहाध्वजम् रथंराक्षसराजस्यनरराजोददर्श ह ।कृष्णवाजिसमायुक्तंयुक्तंरौद्रेणवर्चसा दीप्यमानमिवाकाशेविमानंसूर्यवर्चसं ।तडित्पताकागहनंदर्शितेन्द्रायुधप्रभम्","trans":"The chariot bells fixed to the huge flag post were making sounds, yoked to dark horses, and was shining with splendor with rage. It was glowing like a bright sun in the sky displaying its splendor, like the aerial chariot. It looked like a cloud holding water, releasing water of arrows from Rakshasa king's bow. The king of humans saw this chariot.","words":[{"d":"स्वनवन्तम्","m":"bells making sounds"},{"d":"महाध्वजम्","m":"huge flag post"},{"d":"कृष्णवाजिसमायुक्तम्","m":"yoked to dark horses"},{"d":"रौद्रेण","m":"enraged"},{"d":"वर्चसा","m":"splendor"},{"d":"युक्तम्","m":"fixed"},{"d":"आकाशे","m":"sky"},{"d":"दीप्यमानम्","m":"glowing"},{"d":"विमानमिव","m":"like the aerial chariot"},{"d":"सूर्यवर्चसम्","m":"bright like sun"},{"d":"तडित्पताकागहनम्","m":"shining in the sky"},{"d":"दर्शितेन्द्रायुथप्रभम्","m":"displaying its splendor"},{"d":"सहसा","m":"with force"},{"d":"आपतन्तम्","m":"cloud with water"},{"d":"तम्","m":"from"},{"d":"राक्षसराजस्य","m":"Rakshasa king's"},{"d":"रथम्","m":"chariot"},{"d":"नरराजः","m":"king of humans"},{"d":"ददर्श ह","m":"saw"}]},{"v":5,"dev":"समापतन्तंसहसास्वनवन्तंमहाध्वजम् रथंराक्षसराजस्यनरराजोददर्श ह ।कृष्णवाजिसमायुक्तंयुक्तंरौद्रेणवर्चसा दीप्यमानमिवाकाशेविमानंसूर्यवर्चसं ।तडित्पताकागहनंदर्शितेन्द्रायुधप्रभम्","trans":"The chariot bells fixed to the huge flag post were making sounds, yoked to dark horses, and was shining with splendor with rage. It was glowing like a bright sun in the sky displaying its splendor, like the aerial chariot. It looked like a cloud holding water, releasing water of arrows from Rakshasa king's bow. The king of humans saw this chariot.","words":[{"d":"स्वनवन्तम्","m":"bells making sounds"},{"d":"महाध्वजम्","m":"huge flag post"},{"d":"कृष्णवाजिसमायुक्तम्","m":"yoked to dark horses"},{"d":"रौद्रेण","m":"enraged"},{"d":"वर्चसा","m":"splendor"},{"d":"युक्तम्","m":"fixed"},{"d":"आकाशे","m":"sky"},{"d":"दीप्यमानम्","m":"glowing"},{"d":"विमानमिव","m":"like the aerial chariot"},{"d":"सूर्यवर्चसम्","m":"bright like sun"},{"d":"तडित्पताकागहनम्","m":"shining in the sky"},{"d":"दर्शितेन्द्रायुथप्रभम्","m":"displaying its splendor"},{"d":"सहसा","m":"with force"},{"d":"आपतन्तम्","m":"cloud with water"},{"d":"तम्","m":"from"},{"d":"राक्षसराजस्य","m":"Rakshasa king's"},{"d":"रथम्","m":"chariot"},{"d":"नरराजः","m":"king of humans"},{"d":"ददर्श ह","m":"saw"}]},{"v":6,"dev":"समापतन्तंसहसास्वनवन्तंमहाध्वजम् रथंराक्षसराजस्यनरराजोददर्श ह ।कृष्णवाजिसमायुक्तंयुक्तंरौद्रेणवर्चसा दीप्यमानमिवाकाशेविमानंसूर्यवर्चसं ।तडित्पताकागहनंदर्शितेन्द्रायुधप्रभम्","trans":"The chariot bells fixed to the huge flag post were making sounds, yoked to dark horses, and was shining with splendor with rage. It was glowing like a bright sun in the sky displaying its splendor, like the aerial chariot. It looked like a cloud holding water, releasing water of arrows from Rakshasa king's bow. The king of humans saw this chariot.","words":[{"d":"स्वनवन्तम्","m":"bells making sounds"},{"d":"महाध्वजम्","m":"huge flag post"},{"d":"कृष्णवाजिसमायुक्तम्","m":"yoked to dark horses"},{"d":"रौद्रेण","m":"enraged"},{"d":"वर्चसा","m":"splendor"},{"d":"युक्तम्","m":"fixed"},{"d":"आकाशे","m":"sky"},{"d":"दीप्यमानम्","m":"glowing"},{"d":"विमानमिव","m":"like the aerial chariot"},{"d":"सूर्यवर्चसम्","m":"bright like sun"},{"d":"तडित्पताकागहनम्","m":"shining in the sky"},{"d":"दर्शितेन्द्रायुथप्रभम्","m":"displaying its splendor"},{"d":"सहसा","m":"with force"},{"d":"आपतन्तम्","m":"cloud with water"},{"d":"तम्","m":"from"},{"d":"राक्षसराजस्य","m":"Rakshasa king's"},{"d":"रथम्","m":"chariot"},{"d":"नरराजः","m":"king of humans"},{"d":"ददर्श ह","m":"saw"}]},{"v":7,"dev":"शराधाराविमुञ्चन्तंधारासारमिवाम्बुदम् ।तंदृष्टवामेघसङ्काशमापतन्तंरथंरिपोः गिरेर्वज्राभिमृष्टस्यदीर्यतस्सदृशस्वनम् ।विस्पारयन्वैवेगेनबालचन्द्रानतंधनुः उवाचसारथिंरामंसहस्राक्षस्यमातलिम् ।","trans":"The flow of arrows (from Ravana) released from the chariot were seen by Rama like the flow of water from rain clouds. Seeing that, Sri Rama made terrific sounds by stretching his bow to crescent shape, and it was as if a mountain struck by thunderbolt had broken and resounding and seeing Matali, charioteer of Indra, Sri Rama spoke as follows.","words":[{"d":"शरधाराः","m":"flow of arrows"},{"d":"विमुञ्चन्तम्","m":"released from"},{"d":"धारासारमिवा","m":"like the flow of water"},{"d":"अम्बुदमिव","m":"like rain water cloud"},{"d":"मेघसङ्काशम्","m":"from the clouds"},{"d":"वज्राभिमृष्टस्य","m":"struck by thunderbolt"},{"d":"दीर्यतः","m":"broken"},{"d":"गिरेः","m":"mountain"},{"d":"सदृशस्वनम्","m":"like sound of mountain"},{"d":"आपतन्तम्","m":"cloud"},{"d":"तम्","m":"him"},{"d":"रथम्","m":"chariot"},{"d":"दृष्टवा","m":"seeing"},{"d":"रामः","m":"Rama"},{"d":"बालचन्द्रानतम्","m":"crescent shaped like the young moon"},{"d":"धनुः","m":"bow"},{"d":"वेगेन","m":"with speed"},{"d":"विस्फारयन्","m":"stretching"},{"d":"सहस्राक्षस्यसारथिम्","m":"Indra's charioteer"},{"d":"मातलिम्","m":"Matali"},{"d":"उवाच","m":"spoke"}]},{"v":8,"dev":"शराधाराविमुञ्चन्तंधारासारमिवाम्बुदम् ।तंदृष्टवामेघसङ्काशमापतन्तंरथंरिपोः गिरेर्वज्राभिमृष्टस्यदीर्यतस्सदृशस्वनम् ।विस्पारयन्वैवेगेनबालचन्द्रानतंधनुः उवाचसारथिंरामंसहस्राक्षस्यमातलिम् ।","trans":"The flow of arrows (from Ravana) released from the chariot were seen by Rama like the flow of water from rain clouds. Seeing that, Sri Rama made terrific sounds by stretching his bow to crescent shape, and it was as if a mountain struck by thunderbolt had broken and resounding and seeing Matali, charioteer of Indra, Sri Rama spoke as follows.","words":[{"d":"शरधाराः","m":"flow of arrows"},{"d":"विमुञ्चन्तम्","m":"released from"},{"d":"धारासारमिवा","m":"like the flow of water"},{"d":"अम्बुदमिव","m":"like rain water cloud"},{"d":"मेघसङ्काशम्","m":"from the clouds"},{"d":"वज्राभिमृष्टस्य","m":"struck by thunderbolt"},{"d":"दीर्यतः","m":"broken"},{"d":"गिरेः","m":"mountain"},{"d":"सदृशस्वनम्","m":"like sound of mountain"},{"d":"आपतन्तम्","m":"cloud"},{"d":"तम्","m":"him"},{"d":"रथम्","m":"chariot"},{"d":"दृष्टवा","m":"seeing"},{"d":"रामः","m":"Rama"},{"d":"बालचन्द्रानतम्","m":"crescent shaped like the young moon"},{"d":"धनुः","m":"bow"},{"d":"वेगेन","m":"with speed"},{"d":"विस्फारयन्","m":"stretching"},{"d":"सहस्राक्षस्यसारथिम्","m":"Indra's charioteer"},{"d":"मातलिम्","m":"Matali"},{"d":"उवाच","m":"spoke"}]},{"v":9,"dev":"मातलेपश्यसम्रद्धमापतन्तंरथंरिपोः यथापसव्यंपततावेगेनमहतापुनः ।समरेहन्तुमात्मानंतथानेनकृतामतिः","trans":"\"Matali! the enemy's chariot is darting forward hurriedly. See him coming in the reverse direction with great speed once again. It strikes my mind that he is surely causing his fall.\"","words":[{"d":"मातले","m":"Matali"},{"d":"सम्रद्धम्","m":"hurrying"},{"d":"आपतन्तम्","m":"darting forward"},{"d":"रिपोः","m":"enemy"},{"d":"रथम्","m":"chariot"},{"d":"पश्य","m":"seeing"},{"d":"अपसव्यम्","m":"in reverse direction"},{"d":"महता","m":"great"},{"d":"वेगेन","m":"with speed"},{"d":"पुनः","m":"once again"},{"d":"पतता","m":"causing a fall"},{"d":"समरे","m":"in war"},{"d":"आत्मानम्","m":"himself"},{"d":"हन्तुम्","m":"to kill"},{"d":"यथा","m":"that way"},{"d":"तथानेन","m":"like that"},{"d":"मतिः","m":"mind"},{"d":"कृता","m":"strikes me"}]},{"v":10,"dev":"मातलेपश्यसम्रद्धमापतन्तंरथंरिपोः यथापसव्यंपततावेगेनमहतापुनः ।समरेहन्तुमात्मानंतथानेनकृतामतिः","trans":"\"Matali! the enemy's chariot is darting forward hurriedly. See him coming in the reverse direction with great speed once again. It strikes my mind that he is surely causing his fall.\"","words":[{"d":"मातले","m":"Matali"},{"d":"सम्रद्धम्","m":"hurrying"},{"d":"आपतन्तम्","m":"darting forward"},{"d":"रिपोः","m":"enemy"},{"d":"रथम्","m":"chariot"},{"d":"पश्य","m":"seeing"},{"d":"अपसव्यम्","m":"in reverse direction"},{"d":"महता","m":"great"},{"d":"वेगेन","m":"with speed"},{"d":"पुनः","m":"once again"},{"d":"पतता","m":"causing a fall"},{"d":"समरे","m":"in war"},{"d":"आत्मानम्","m":"himself"},{"d":"हन्तुम्","m":"to kill"},{"d":"यथा","m":"that way"},{"d":"तथानेन","m":"like that"},{"d":"मतिः","m":"mind"},{"d":"कृता","m":"strikes me"}]},{"v":11,"dev":"तदप्रमादमातिष्ठन्प्रत्युद्गच्छरथंरिपोः ।विध्वंसयितुमिच्छामिवायुर्मेघमिवोत्थितम्","trans":"\"Being alert, you drive the chariot towards Ravana, just as wind drives the cloud in the sky, as I wish to destroy him.\"","words":[{"d":"तत्","m":"then"},{"d":"अप्रमादम्","m":"being alert"},{"d":"अतिष्ठ","m":"staying"},{"d":"रिपोः","m":"enemy"},{"d":"रथम्","m":"chariot"},{"d":"प्रत्युद्गच्छ","m":"towards him"},{"d":"वायुः","m":"wind"},{"d":"उत्थितम्","m":"excessively rising"},{"d":"मेघमिव","m":"like cloud"},{"d":"विध्वंसयितुम्","m":"destroy him"},{"d":"इ च्छामि","m":"wish to"}]},{"v":12,"dev":"अविक्लबमसम्भ्रान्तमव्यग्रहृदयेक्षणम् ।रमशिसञ्चारनियंप्रचोदयरथंद्रुतम्","trans":"\"Drive the chariot swiftly without confusion, without any agitation, with steady heart and vision, controlling the movement of reins and determination.","words":[{"d":"अविक्लबम्","m":"without confusion"},{"d":"असम्भ्रान्तम्","m":"without agitation"},{"d":"अव्यग्रहृदयेक्षणम्","m":"with steady heart and vision"},{"d":"रमशिसञ्चारनियतम्","m":"movement of reins controlled"},{"d":"रथम्","m":"chariot"},{"d":"द्रुतम्","m":"determined"},{"d":"प्रचोदय","m":"drive swiftly"}]},{"v":13,"dev":"कामं न त्वंसमाधेयःपुरन्दररथोचितः ।युयुत्सुरहमेकाग्रःस्मारयेत्वां न शिक्ष्ये","trans":"\"You are a driver of great Indra's chariot. You are not required to be told. Wishing to fight with rapt attention, I will remind you now and then not instruct you\", said Rama to Matali.\"","words":[{"d":"पुरन्दररथोचितः","m":"driver of the chariot of one like Indra"},{"d":"त्वम्","m":"you"},{"d":"कामम्","m":"desire"},{"d":"न समाधेयः","m":"not required to be told"},{"d":"अहम्","m":"by me"},{"d":"एकाग्रः","m":"single pointed"},{"d":"युयुत्सुः","m":"wishing to fight"},{"d":"त्वाम्","m":"you"},{"d":"स्मारये","m":"remind you"},{"d":"न शिक्ष्ये","m":"not instruct"}]},{"v":14,"dev":"परितुष्टः स रामस्यतेनवाक्येनमातलिः ।प्रचोदयामासरथंसुरसारथिरुत्तमः","trans":"Matali, the best charioteer of the Devatas, was highly delighted at Rama's words and started driving.","words":[{"d":"उत्तमः","m":"best"},{"d":"सुरसारथिः","m":"charioteer of Devatas"},{"d":"सः","m":"he"},{"d":"मातलिः","m":"Matali"},{"d":"रामस्य","m":"Rama's"},{"d":"तेनवाक्येन","m":"by his words"},{"d":"परितुष्टः","m":"highly delighted"},{"d":"रथम्","m":"chariot"},{"d":"प्रचोदयामास","m":"started driving."}]},{"v":15,"dev":"अपसव्यंततःकुर्वन् रावणस्यमहारथम् ।चक्रसम्भूतरसारावणंव्यवदूनयन्","trans":"Then Matali made the chariot turn round and by the dust rising from the rolling wheels of the chariot, Ravana was shaken.","words":[{"d":"ततः","m":"then"},{"d":"रावणस्य","m":"Ravana's"},{"d":"रथम्","m":"chariot"},{"d":"अपसव्यम्","m":"turned"},{"d":"कुर्वन्","m":"done"},{"d":"चक्रसम्भूतरजसा","m":"dust arising out of rolling wheels"},{"d":"रावणम्","m":"Ravana"},{"d":"व्यवधूनयन्","m":"shaken"}]},{"v":16,"dev":"ततःक्रुद्धोदशग्रीवस्ताम्रविस्फारितेक्षणः ।रथप्रतिमुखंरामंसायकैरवधूनयत्","trans":"Then furious Ravana, the ten headed Rakshasa, whose eyes turned coppery in anger, struck Rama with arrows.","words":[{"d":"ततः","m":"then"},{"d":"दशग्रीवः","m":"ten headed"},{"d":"ताम्रविस्फारितेक्षणः","m":"coppery eyes open widely"},{"d":"रामम्","m":"Rama"},{"d":"सायकैः","m":"arrows"},{"d":"अवधूनयत्","m":"struck"}]},{"v":17,"dev":"धर्षणामर्षितोरामोधैर्यंरोषेणलम्भयन् ।जग्राहसुमहावेगमैन्द्रंयुधिशरासनम्","trans":"Rama who was provoked by the assault and army was perturbed. He took up Indra's bow of extraordinary impulse and of high speed like sunbeams.","words":[{"d":"धर्षणामर्षितः","m":"provoked by the assault"},{"d":"रामः","m":"Rama"},{"d":"सैन्यम्","m":"army"},{"d":"रोषेण","m":"perturbed"},{"d":"लम्भयन्","m":"of extraordinary impulse"},{"d":"युधि","m":"bow"},{"d":"सुमहावेगम्","m":"at high speed"},{"d":"ऐन्द्रम्","m":"Indra's"},{"d":"शरासनम्","m":"like sunbeams"},{"d":"जग्राह","m":"took up"}]},{"v":18,"dev":"शरांश्चसुमहावेगान्सूर्यरश्मिसमप्रभान् ।तदुपोढुंमहद्युद्धमन्योन्यवधकाङ्क्षिणोः परस्पराभिमुखयोर्दृप्तयोरिवसिंहयोः ।","trans":"The arrows endowed with very high speed, glowing in radiance like the sun's radiance, holding the arrows, each one desirous of killing the other stood facing each other, came near, and started fighting like lions in the great war.","words":[{"d":"सुमहावेगान्","m":"of very high speed"},{"d":"सूर्यरश्मिसमप्रभान्","m":"glowing in radiance like the sun's rays"},{"d":"शरान् च","m":"arrows"},{"d":"अन्योन्यवधकाङ्क्षिणोः","m":"each one desirous killing the other"},{"d":"तत्","m":"then"},{"d":"महत्","m":"great"},{"d":"युद्धम्","m":"war"},{"d":"परस्पराभिमुखयोः","m":"who stood facing each other"},{"d":"दृप्तयोः","m":"ensued"},{"d":"सिंहयोरिव","m":"like lions"},{"d":"उपोढम्","m":"come near"